headline: Is Interactive Brokers Group Worth a Closer Look After Year-to-Date 40.7% Gain?
summary: Wondering if Interactive Brokers Group is a bargain or just fairly priced? You are not alone. Figuring out what the stock is truly worth has plenty of investors curious right now. Shares have had a rollercoaster ride lately, climbing 5.1% in the last week, pulling back 7.2% over the past month, but up an impressive 40.7% year-to-date and 34.9% in the last year.
